OL,7,FHundreds more specialist nurses are
OL,8,Fneeded to cope with the rise in
OL,9,Fnumber of people looking for help and
OL,10,Fsupport with dementia, the head of a
OL,11,Fleading charity has warned.
OL,13,FDr Hilda Hayo, chief executive at
OL,14,FDementia UK, has appealed for "urgent
OL,15,Finvestment" from the Government to
OL,16,Fsupport an ageing population with
OL,17,Fmultiple complex needs. Some 944,000
OL,18,Fpeople in the UK are living with
OL,19,Fdementia, a figure that is expected
OL,20,Fto rise to more than one million by
OL,21,F2025
OL,3,CSpecialist dementia nurses need to
OL,4,Cdouble to cope with surge in
OL,5,Cpatients, charity head warns
